title: 136: The Trader Joe’s Haul Episode (Meal Hacks Edition!)
itunes:title: The Trader Joe’s Haul Episode (Meal Hacks Edition!)
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa, Mikey, and Jamie are tasting some of the best and healthiest meal starters at Trader Joe’s! Finds like a multigrain vegetable medley, chimichurri rice, langostino tails, the popular shakshuka starter, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus Lisa reveals the 50-calories-a-serving find of all finds! So grab that grocery bag, push the play button, and take a trip to Trader Joe’s with us on Chew the Right Thing! For a list of all the finds mentioned in the episode, head on over to our Foodcast page!
itunes:summary: You asked for it, so here it is… MEAL HACK finds from the Trader we call Joe!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
